    <summary>AI-powered terminal color palette generator with preference learning</summary>
    <description>
Claude Color is an AI-powered CLI tool for generating beautiful, accessible color palettes.

Features:
- Generate palettes using color theory schemes (complementary, analogous, triadic, etc.)
- AI-powered palette generation from natural language descriptions
- Extract colors from images and websites
- Personalized recommendations based on your preferences
- Interactive TUI palette editor
- Export to CSS, Sass, Tailwind, and more
- Favorites management with tags and search
- WCAG accessibility compliance checking
- Preference learning for personalized suggestions
    </description>
